OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779793371
OL,3,CTeenager missing after entering
OL,4,CSwanholme Lakes
OL,6,FA teenage boy is missing after
OL,7,Fentering Swanholme Lakes in Lincoln.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,10,Farea at 2.30pm on Sunday 24 May,
OL,11,Ffollowing reports of a boy getting
OL,12,Finto trouble in the water.
OL,14,FPolice said at 4:40pm on Sunday:
OL,15,F"Despite the very best efforts of
OL,16,Fpeople at the lake and the emergency
OL,17,Fservices who arrived on scene, the boy
OL,18,Fhas not yet been located.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
