OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779793371
OL,3,CTeenager missing after entering
OL,4,CSwanholme Lakes
OL,6,F"We continue to search the lake and
OL,7,Four Under Water Search Team will be
OL,8,Fassisting with this.
OL,10,F"We have informed the family of the
OL,11,Fboy and our thoughts are with them at
OL,12,Fthis incredibly difficult time.
OL,14,F"It is vitally important that people
OL,15,Fdo not speculate or share information
OL,16,Fthat is not accurate. Information that
OL,17,Fthe boy has been found at this time is
OL,18,Fwrong. We will update our information
OL,19,Fwhen we can."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU{D@MO]
